Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:54.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:03:00.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:08.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}风沙遮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:15.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你渐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}无论何时 都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}即便一切 天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}唯有那件 唯有那件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}日常之事 不曾改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:28.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}看一看吧 那充满光芒的唯一
